<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْد ُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<span class="c5"> سَأَلْتُ مَعْمَرًا:</span> هَلْ يَتَزَوَّجُ الرَّجُلُ امْرَأَةَ رَبِيبِهِ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا بَأْسَ بِهَا»</span>،<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> فَابْنَةَ رَبِيبِهِ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا تَحِلُّ لَهُ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>